column3: 'di ni 'du byed kyi phung po zhes bya'o // / +rnam par shes pa gang zhe na / / +dmigs pa rnam par rig pa'o // /
sems dang yid kyang de yin te // / +sna tshogs pa dang yid rten byed pa'i phyir ro / / +dngos su na  sems ni kun gzhi rnam par shes pa ste / /

rigs gcig pa dang  rgyun chags par 'jug pa'o // / +'di ltar 'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa  dang  'du shes med pa'i snyoms bar 'jug pa dang  pa rnams langs nas yang yul rnam par rig pa zhes bya ba 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa 'byung ba dang  dmigs pa'i rkyen la ltos nas rnam pa gzhan du 'jug pa nyid dang  chad nas yang 'byung ba  nyid dang  'khor bar 'jug pa dang  ldog pa'i phyir ro // /
column4: 5.960#TD4067E.TXT.r#1095200#1095202#TD4067E.TXT.r_1494# 'di LTAR 'GOG PA'I SNYOMS PAR 'JUG PA DANG  'du SHES MED PA'I SNYOMS PAR 'JUG PA DANG  'du shes med pa rnams las langs nas  YUL RNAM PAR RIG PA ZHES BYA BA 'JUG PA'I RNAM PAR SHES PA 'BYUNG BA DANG DMIGS PA'I RKYEN LA LTOS NAS ZHES bya ba ste / /

column3: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa de nyid ni sa bon thams cad kyi gzhi nyid dang  lus kyi kun gzhi dang  rgyu nyid dang  lus la gnas pa nyid kyi yang phyir ro // /
column4: 0.0#TD4067E.TXT.r#1095328#1095330#TD4067E.TXT.r_1512;TD4067E.TXT.r_1513# de lta bu'i rang bzhin can gyi lus kyi rgyu'i bye brag ni KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA ZHES bya'o // / +KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA DE    NYID NI SA BON THAMS CAD KYI GZHI NYID DANG  LUS KYI KUN GZHI DANG RGYU NYID CES bya ba ni 'di ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos thams cad kyi sa bon gang yin pa de dag de la gnas te / /
column5: 0.025#TD4068E.TXT.r#600362#600362#TD4068E.TXT.r_3479;TD4068E.TXT.r_3480# kun gzhi  RNAM PAR SHES PA LA ci'i phyir KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA ZHES bya ba'i don bstan par bya ba'i phyir / / +KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA NYID NI SA BON THAMS CAD KYI KUN GZHI DANG ZHES bya ba smos te / /

column3: len pa'i rnam par shes pa yang de yin te / / +lus  len pa'i phyir ro // / +dngos su ni yid ni kun gzhi rnam par shes pa la dmigs te / /
column4: 0.029#TD4066E.TXT.r#2116863#2116863#TD4066E.TXT.r_2069;TD4066E.TXT.r_2070# de lta BAS KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA NYID nying mtshams sbyor ba'i dus nas lus bzung nas  shi ba la thug gi bar du lus mtha' dag la brten te 'byung bas de nyid nying mtshams sbyor ba nas shi ba la thug gi bar du lus 'dzin pas na LEN PA'I RNAM PAR SHES PA ZHES bya'o // / +dngos su na YID KUN GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA LA DMIGS ZHES bya ba ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kun    GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA LA RTAG par bdag tu dmigs te / /

column3: rtag tu bdag tu rmongs pa dang / / +bdag tu lta ba dang  bdag tu nga rgyal dang  bdag la chags pa la sogs pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i rnam par shes pa ste / /
column4: 0.017#TD4066E.TXT.r#2116879#2116879#TD4066E.TXT.r_2070;TD4066E.TXT.r_2071# dngos su na yid kun GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA LA dmigs zhes bya ba ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kun    GZHI RNAM PAR SHES PA LA rtag par bdag tu dmigs te / / +bdag tu rmongs pa dang  lta ba dang  nga rgyal dang  chags par dmigs pa rnams DANG MTSHUNGS BAR LDAN PA'I phyir ro // /
column5: 0.022#TD4033E.TXT.r#1385796#1385797#TD4033E.TXT.r_674# myong ba'i don dang ni sems de nyid KYIS BDAG TU RMONGS PA DANG  bdag tu lta ba dang  BDAG TU NGA RGYAL DANG  BDAG LA CHAGS PA DANG   myong ba'i don yin pa'i phyir ro // /
column6: 0.023#TD4079E.TXT.r#758528#758529#TD4079E.TXT.r_302;TD4079E.TXT.r_303# gyi rten du gyur pas kun gzhi yin la rang gi ngo bo la nye bar dmigs PAS RNAM PAR SHES PA'O // / +bdag tu rmongs pa dang  bdag tu lta ba dang  BDAG LA CHAGS PA DANG  BDAG TU NGA RGYAL BA ste / /
column7: 0.024#TD4068E.TXT.r#601456#601457#TD4068E.TXT.r_3582# rtag tu bdag tu gti mug pa dang   bdag tu lta ba dang  BDAG TU NGA RGYAL BA dang  BDAG LA CHAGS PA LA SOGS PA DANG MTSHUNGS PAR LDAN ZHES bya ba smos te / /

column3: rigs gcig  pa dang  rgyun chags par 'jug pa ste / / +dgra bcom pa dang  'phags pa'i lam dang  'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa'i dus ma gtogs so / /
column4: 0.028#TD4066E.TXT.r#2117008#2117008#TD4066E.TXT.r_2090;TD4066E.TXT.r_2091# dgra bcom pa dang  'phags pa'i lam dang  'gog pa'i  SNYOMS PAR 'JUG PA'I DUS MA GTOGS SO // / +dgra bcom pa ni khams gsum pa'i nyon mongs pa can gyi chos spangs pa'i phyir dgra bcom pa'i dus ni mi 'byung ngo // /

column41: 0.020#TD4005E.TXT.r#552784#552784#TD4005E.TXT.r_550;TD4005E.TXT.r_551# slob dpon chen po 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'anta rakshi ta dang  bod kyi lo ts'a ba rnyi ba de ba gho sha SA BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa'o // /
column42: 0.021#TD4014E.TXT.r#442259#442260#TD4014E.TXT.r_880;TD4014E.TXT.r_881# 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam gyi rgyal po'i rgya cher 'grel ba slob dpon rgyan bzang pos mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya GAR GYI MKHAN PO DZNY'A NA garbha DANG ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BAN DE KA ba dpal brtsegs rakshi tas bsgyur te bstan la phab pa'o // /
column43: 0.022#TD4020E.TXT.r#2533600#2533600#TD4020E.TXT.r_3317;TD4020E.TXT.r_3318# theg pa chen po mdo sde'i rgyan ces bya ba'i tshig le'ur byas pa 'phags pa byams pas mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'akya sim ha dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BANDE dpal brtsegs LA SOGS PAS BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN  la phab pa / /
column44: 0.022#TD4022E.TXT.r#398833#398833#TD4022E.TXT.r_142;TD4022E.TXT.r_143# chos dang chos nyid rnam par 'byed pa 'phags pa byams pas mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya GAR GYI MKHAN PO PANDI ta sh'anti bha dra dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA DGE slong tshul khrims rgyal  BAS BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa las / /
column45: 0.022#TD4029E.TXT.r#2165510#2165510#TD4029E.TXT.r_5921;TD4029E.TXT.r_5922# slob dpon ngo bo nyid med pas mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'akya sim ha dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BANDE dpal brtsegs KYIS BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa'o //// /
column46: 0.022#TD4076E.TXT.r#2188613#2188613#TD4076E.TXT.r_119;TD4076E.TXT.r_120# slob dpon mkhas pa rin chen po rin chen 'byung gnas zhi ba'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'an ti bha dra dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA 'GOS lhas btsas KYIS BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa //// /
column47: 0.023#TD4078E.TXT.r#680363#680364#TD4078E.TXT.r_115;TD4078E.TXT.r_116# shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom pa'i man ngag slob dpon chen po ratna aa ka ra sh'an tis mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya GAR GYI MKHAN PO CHEN po dpal rab 'byor zhi ba dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA DGE slong ting nge 'dzin bzang pos  BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa // /
column48: 0.023#TD4004E.TXT.r#106900#106901#TD4004E.TXT.r_239;TD4004E.TXT.r_240# slob dpon zhi ba lhas mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya gar gyi mkhan po dharma r'a dza dang  bod kyi lo ts'a ba 'phags pa shes rab kyis bsgyur ba'o // /
column49: 0.023#TD4045E.TXT.r#397922#397923#TD4045E.TXT.r_404;TD4045E.TXT.r_405# byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims kyi le'u bshad pa slob dpon yon tan 'od  kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so //// / +rgya GAR GYI MKHAN PO PRA dzny'a wa rma dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BENDE YE SHES SDE LA SOGS PAS BSGYUR CING ZHUS TE GTAN la phab pa'o // /
column50: 0.024#TD4042E.TXT.r#1683925#1683925#TD4042E.TXT.r_882# RGYA GAR GYI MKHAN PO PRA dzny'a wa rma dang  SU RENDRA BO DHI DANG  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BAN DE YE SHES SDES zhus te gtan pa phab pa / /
column51: 0.024#TD4057E.TXT.r#1399834#1399834#TD4057E.TXT.r_337# RGYA GAR GYI MKHAN PO DZI NA MI TRA DANG  sh'i len dra bo dhi dang  ZHU CHEN GYI LO TS'A BA BAN DE YE SHES SDES zhus te gtan la phab pa // /
